 theo lý thuyết có thể bị nhiễm tới bốn lần.</p><a class="mt-auto inline-block pb-[4px] text-text-link" href="/benh/sot-xuat-huyet-dengue-155.html"><span class="css-15sc8tc flex items-center">Tìm hiểu thêm<style data-emotion="css wi4pw5">.css-wi4pw5{display:inline-block;vertical-align:-0.125em;}.css-wi4pw5 svg{width:20px;height:20px;}</style><span size="20" class="estore-icon ml-[4px] css-wi4pw5"><svg viewBox="0 0 25 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M9.25383 4.29289C8.86331 4.68342 8.86331 5.31658 9.25383 5.70711L15.5467 12L9.25383 18.2929C8.86331 18.6834 8.86331 19.3166 9.25383 19.7071C9.64436 20.0976 10.2775 20.0976 10.668 19.7071L17.668 12.7071C18.0586 12.3166 18.0586 11.6834 17.668 11.2929L10.668 4.29289C10.2775 3.90237 9.64435 3.90237 9.25383 4.29289Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></span></a></div></div></div><div class="styles_embla__slide__JiX50"><div class="flex h-full w-full flex-col rounded-[8px] bg-white transition-all md:rounded-xl md:p-[16px]" style="box-shadow:0px 0px 24px -4px rgba(0, 39, 102, 0.08), 0px 0px 8px -4px rgba(0, 39, 102, 0.03)"><a class="flex" href="/benh/ebola-438.html"><div class="css-wquh38"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-t-[8px] rounded-b-[0px] md:rounded-[8px]"><picture class="!h-full w-full object-cover"><source srcSet="https://cdn.nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/unsafe/257x152/https://cms-prod.s3-sgn09.fptcloud.com/ebola_073e9acd59.png" type="image/webp" width="257" height="152"/><source srcSet="/estore-images/fallback-images/default/img-default-16_9.svg" type="image/webp" width="257" height="152"/><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="Ebola" class="!h-full w-full object-cover" src="/estore-images/fallback-images/error/img-error-16_9.svg"/></picture></div></div></a><div class="flex h-full grow flex-col p-[12px] md:p-0 md:pt-[20px]"><h3 class="css-177jx5p leading-[24px] tracking-[0.005em] text-text-primary md:tracking-[0.0025em]">Ebola</h3><p class="css-5gg2ui mt-[8px] mb-[24px] text-gray-7 lin